OL,3,CAndy Murray to coach Britain's Jack
OL,4,CDraper ahead of Wimbledon
OL,6,FAndy Murray is making a return to the
OL,7,Ftennis world to coach Britain's Jack
OL,8,FDraper this grass-court season,
OL,9,Fincluding Wimbledon 2026.
OL,11,FMurray had six months coaching his
OL,12,Fformer rival, Novak Djokovic, between
OL,13,FNovember 2024 and last May, but had
OL,14,Fsince been away from the sport to
OL,15,Fspend time with his family and on the
OL,16,Fgolf course.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
