OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778637818
OL,3,CAndy Murray to coach Britain's Jack
OL,4,CDraper ahead of Wimbledon
OL,6,FThe Scot said in a recent interview
OL,7,Fthat he was open to having another
OL,8,Fcrack at coaching, and it has now
OL,9,Femerged that he will team up with
OL,10,FBritain's most exciting male prospect
OL,11,Fthis summer.
OL,13,FDraper announced on Tuesday that he
OL,14,Fhas split from tennis coach Jamie
OL,15,FDelgado, saying: "I am very grateful
OL,16,Ffor everything Jamie Delgado has done
OL,17,Ffor me over these past six months. He
OL,18,Fis a world-class coach and a great man.
OL,26,@wD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
