CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778637818
OL,3,CAndy Murray to coach Britain's Jack
OL,4,CDraper ahead of Wimbledon
OL,6,F"In the interim, I will continue to be
OL,7,Fsupported by the excellent team at the
OL,8,FLTA (Lawn Tennis Association), with
OL,9,Fthe addition of Andy Murray, who will
OL,10,Fbe supporting me throughout the grass
OL,11,Fcourt season."
OL,13,FWhile Murray's new job is initially a
OL,14,Fshort-term arrangement, the prospect
OL,15,Fof coaching the man described by many
OL,16,Fas his successor in the British sport
OL,17,Fis a hugely exciting one for fans.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]
