CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778637818
OL,3,CAndy Murray to coach Britain's Jack
OL,4,CDraper ahead of Wimbledon
OL,6,F"Injuries are going to happen... we
OL,7,Fare pushing our bodies to do things
OL,8,Fthey aren't supposed to in elite
OL,9,Fsport," he wrote in October in a post
OL,10,Fon X.
OL,12,F"We have so many incredible younger
OL,13,Fguys on the tour right now and I'm
OL,14,Fproud to be a part of that, however,
OL,15,Fthe tour and the calendar have to
OL,16,Fadapt if any of us are gonna achieve
OL,17,Fsome sort of longevity."
